<jsp:include page="/WEB-INF/header.jsp" />
	<div id="Policy1">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="col-md-6 wow bounceInLeft">
				<p class="header">
				Ratsada! Policy
				</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div id="Policy2">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<div align="center" id="A" class="wow bounceInDown"><p class="policy1">30 Days Free Return</p><hr style="border-top: 1px solid #ccc;"></div>
				<br>
				<p class="main1">
				<b>1. THE Ratsada! PROMISE</b><br>
				We offer convenient and hassle-free shopping!<br>
				<br>
				SATISFACTION GUARANTEED : Free returns within 30 days - no questions asked<br>
				AUTHENTICITY GUARANTEED : Cash refund if you have any doubts<br>
				RISK FREE SHOPPING : Our payment options are safe and secure<br>
				<br>
				At Ratsada!, we want you to be happy with every purchase. If you are dissatisfied with the item, we offer free & easy returns - no questions asked. Need a different size? Exchange it for free!
				<br><br>
				Items purchased at Ratsada! can be returned within 30 days of delivery provided they have not been used and are in their original packaging.
				<br><br>
				All our items are new, authentic, and shipped in excellent condition. Should you encounter a defective item, it will be replaced without question.
				<br><br><br>
				<b>2. HOW TO RETURN AN ITEM?</b><br><br>
				<u>STEP 1: PACK YOUR ITEMS</u><br>
				<br>
				Please fill in the Return Slip you received with your shipment.<br>
				<br>
				Place the item(s) in their original product packaging (box or pouch) and insert return slip and any document that came with the products before sealing your item/s.
				<br><br>
				<u>STEP 2. RETURN YOUR Ratsada! ITEM/S</u><br>
				<br>
				A. DROP-OFF<br>
				Free package drop off at any LBC, 2Go. Indicate the Ratsada! account number:<br>
				<br>
				LBC : 102708<br>
				2GO : 2013100087<br>
				<br>
				B. PICK-UP<br>
				For Metro Manila, Cebu, Metro Zamboanga and Davao only, you may schedule a free pick-up by simply sending an email at pickup@Ratsada!.com.ph, with the ff details:
				<br><br>
				SKU and name of item/s for pickup<br>
				Order Number<br>
				Pickup schedule & address<br>
				Reason for return and option preference<br>
				Details of item for exchange<br>
				(change size/color) if applicable<br>
				<br>
				<u>STEP 3: GET YOUR EXCHANGE ITEM/ REFUND</u><br>
				<br>
				Email notification will be sent within 7 days once the returned item reaches our warehouse.<br>
				<br>
				FOR EXCHANGES: Once returned items reach our warehouse it will undergo quality checking. After which, order for exchange will be processed. The same delivery lead time applies for exchanged items. Total processing time is 7 - 10 days for Metro Manila and 11 - 17 days for provincial from the time you have requested for the exchange until delivery.
				<br><br>
				FOR REFUNDS: Once returned items reach our warehouse it will undergo quality checking. After quality checking, you will receive an email confirmation whether the items passed quality control or not and if refund will be credited to you. Total processing time for refund via Ratsada! wallet credit is 3 to 7 days and 8 - 12 days for other refund methods from the time you have requested the refund.
				<br><br>
				Our Customer Service team is happy to assist you. Call (02) 2305100 should you have any questions or inquiries.
				<br><br>
				<b>3. I need to return an item, but I don't have the original Ratsada! packaging. What now?</b><br>
				Don't fret if you don't have our original Ratsada! packaging (the Ratsada!-branded box or mailer bag) as you can still return the item but please wrap it, so that the original brand packaging and the returned items do not get damaged. All items need to be returned in the original branded product packaging.
				</p>
				
				<br><br><br>
				
				<div align="center" id="B" class="wow bounceInDown"><p class="policy1">Free Delivery & Shipping</p><hr style="border-top: 1px solid #ccc;"></div>
				<br>
				<p class="main1">
				It is the mission of Ratsada! to delivery or ship your order/s for FREE anywhere around the world.
				<br>Your product must be delivered within the next 1-2 hours upon ordering online.
				</p>
				
				<br><br><br>
				
				<div align="center" id="C" class="wow bounceInDown"><p class="policy1">Cash on Delivery Only</p><hr style="border-top: 1px solid #ccc;"></div>
				<br>
				<p class="main1">
				<b>Ratsada! is only accepting Cash On Delivery (COD) Mode of Payment.</b>
				<br>
				Cash on Delivery is a safe and risk-free payment method and you only pay upon receiving your goods. Choosing that payment method also allows your order to be processed faster. Please note that for security purposes you need to pay the Cash On Delivery amount before opening your item. If you don't like the products, you can always return the items afterwards.
				</p>
